                  <value>&quot;Hunger and Boredom&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;Hunger, boredom&quot;</value>
                  <value>&quot;I usually only eat comfort foods when I am bored. I will also eat them when I am happy to celebrate and then when I am sad to comfort me.&quot;</value>
